product.name: Essie Nail Colour Cashmere Matte Collection
product.description:
With a satin-matte texture and a subtle but spellbinding 
micro-iridescent finish, this Essie Nail Colour Cashmere Matte Collection is sure to inspire you to epic 
fashion heights.Features:Soft matte finish with reflective pearl colorLuxurious neutral color palette inspired by rich cashmereFor best results, use without a top coatShades (left to right): Comfy in Cashmere, Wrap Me Up, Just Stitched, All Eyes on Nude, Coat Couture, Spun in Luxe
